  <XenotypeDef>
    <defName>PaccaMechMan_LanceMan</defName>
    <label>Lanceman</label>
    <description>Lancemen are half mechanoid cyborgs that are specialized in long range combat. While they struggle in melee combat, their mechanoid aim assist systems and night vision help ensure their shots land, and their integrated charge lance can potentially pick off a target in a pinch. They are also weak to EMPs.</description>
    <descriptionShort>Lancemen struggle in melee combat, but are very effective with ranged weapons, and can fire a slowly recharging charge lance from their body. They are also weak to EMPs.</descriptionShort>
