  <XenotypeDef>
    <defName>PaccaMechMan_CentiMan</defName>
    <label>Centiman</label>
    <description>Centimen are slow, weak to EMP blasts, and struggle at many tasks, but make up for it by being nearly indestructible in combat. They are nearly immune to fire, completely unaffected by toxins, resistant to temperature swings, rarely bleed out, and that's assuming the damage even makes it past their armor. They perform better then average at both melee and ranged combat, though their slow speed can make it difficult to reposition or retreat. Many xenotypes share horror stories about how waves of Centimen have utterly eradicated colonies.</description>
    <descriptionShort>Centimen are slow, weak to EMPs, and have difficulties performing many common chores, but are extremely robust in combat.</descriptionShort>
